::KitKat::

She heard the transmission. She opened her link,"DarkMouse, I just 
received a transmission. Trace it and deal with it, I am very busy. 
If the bot seek an audiunce, he will have to wait.

DarkMouse:
She sighed and nodded at her link."Yes, I'll go take care of it." she 
said in a less than enthusiastic voice.  She walked out to the 
entrance and looked around. Her scanner read that there was about 
just outside the autogun range. She opened her link to this 
bot. "Approach the entrance and be recongnized." She stood there, 
with her gun in hand, but lowered at her side.
